('95779','33035','5','Generous Dublexwohnung with Harbour View, Palma de Mallorca'),
('95780','33036','5','Located a short walk from the Porto Pi shopping center in Palma de Mallorca away, you will find this spacious penthouse dublex apartment on the 6th and 7th floor. On the lower level of the apartment is the entrance with entrance hall, living-dining room, large kitchen with utility room and storage room, 1 guest bedroom with bathroom en suite and a guest toilet. The upper floor has a gallery, 2 bedrooms each with a bathroom en suite and the master bedroom with bathroom and a terrace. The apartment is equiped with marble floors, parquet floor in the bedrooms, gas central heating, air conditioning, aluminum double glazed windows and a fitted kitchen with dining table. Convenient parking in the underground garage with private parking space is possible.Front of the apartment building there is a comunity Pool and acces to a small marina. Boat moorings for small pleasure boats are in great demand. The seller would be sell his boat, a Sunseeker Monte Rey 27 (7,90m long),equiped with 2 Volvo engines gasoline for € 18,500. The berth can be rented from the city of Palma for about € 650 / year.'),
